1. *Ljuta* se voda prelila iz čaše. (The water spilled angrily from the cup.)
2. *Ljutito* je odmahnuo glavom. (He shook his head angrily.)
3. On je bio *ljut* zbog činjenice da nije uspeo. (He was angry because he failed.)
4. *Ljutilo* ga je što je morao da čeka. (He was angry that he had to wait.)
5. *Ljutiti* su se pogledi između njih sučelili. (Angry glances were exchanged between them.)
6. *Ljutnja* je narasla u njemu. (His anger grew.)